# Milestone Charter v0.7.0

**Project:** RevChatham Homelab

**Milestone:** v0.7.0

**Title:** Operational Backups

**Document Version:** 1.0.0

**Last Reviewed:** 2026-07-14

**Status:** Active

---

# Purpose

Implement a production-inspired operational backup strategy that protects the RevChatham Homelab through verified backups, operational logging, and documented recovery procedures.

This milestone transitions the project from backup planning to operational execution.

---

# References

- ROADMAP.md
- CHANGELOG.md
- ENGINEERING_PRINCIPLES.md
- PROJECT_IMPROVEMENT_REGISTER.md
- BACKUP_RESTORE_RECOVER/

---

# Objectives

The objectives of this milestone are:

- Implement the approved 3-2-1 backup strategy.
- Configure scheduled operational backups.
- Establish operational backup logging.
- Implement backup verification procedures.
- Validate recovery procedures through testing.
- Improve operational visibility through centralized log viewing.

---

# Deliverables

The following deliverables are expected:

- Operational Backup Implementation Plan
- Scheduled Proxmox backups
- Scheduled Docker backups
- Scheduled GitHub repository backups
- Offsite backup implementation
- Backup verification process
- Operational backup logs
- Recovery validation documentation
- Dozzle deployment

---

# Success Criteria

This milestone is successful when:

- The 3-2-1 backup strategy is operational.
- Scheduled backups execute successfully.
- Backup verification is documented.
- Recovery procedures have been validated.
- Operational logs are being generated.
- Backup status can be verified by another administrator.

---

# Risks

Potential risks include:

- Backup storage capacity
- Backup integrity
- Recovery complexity
- Automation failures
- Offsite synchronization issues

Risks will be evaluated throughout the milestone.

---

# Milestone Completion Criteria

This milestone is complete only when:

- All objectives have been completed.
- Deliverables have been produced.
- Documentation has been reviewed for accuracy.
- GitHub repository has passed the repository audit.
- Changes have been committed and pushed.
- Lessons learned have been documented.

---

End of Milestone Charter v0.7.0
